06:29:14.739 --> 06:29:15.839
NSD ignored.

06:29:17.080 --> 06:29:20.263
the major force clause and immediately began three audits.

06:29:21.485 --> 06:29:23.447
MOU finance and instructions.

06:29:24.007 --> 06:29:27.771
