06:32:31.692 --> 06:32:34.133
Unsuccessful dialogue with NSD also.

06:32:34.173 --> 06:32:34.914
That's why we're here.

06:32:35.634 --> 06:32:37.095
We welcome your more questions.

06:32:37.415 --> 06:32:37.695
Thank you.

06:32:43.902 --> 06:32:45.563
Hello, esteemed board members.

06:32:45.643 --> 06:32:48.404
My name is Catherine Polly, a teacher at Beacon.

06:32:49.064 --> 06:32:50.585
